<h2 id="creating-a-main-block-in-python">Creating a Main Block in
Python</h2>
<p>A main block allows you to control the execution of code when a
script is run directly versus when it is imported as a module.</p>
<h3 id="steps">Steps</h3>
<ol type="1">
<li><strong>Add a main block to <code>main.py</code>:</strong></li>
</ol>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb5"><pre
class="sourceCode python"><code class="sourceCode python"><span id="cb5-1"><a href="#cb5-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="co"># src/main.py</span></span>
<span id="cb5-2"><a href="#cb5-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb5-3"><a href="#cb5-3" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="kw">def</span> preprocess_data(data):</span>
<span id="cb5-4"><a href="#cb5-4" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>    <span class="cf">return</span> [x <span class="cf">for</span> x <span class="kw">in</span> data <span class="cf">if</span> x <span class="kw">is</span> <span class="kw">not</span> <span class="va">None</span>]</span>
<span id="cb5-5"><a href="#cb5-5" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb5-6"><a href="#cb5-6" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="cf">if</span> <span class="va">__name__</span> <span class="op">==</span> <span class="st">&quot;__main__&quot;</span>:</span>
<span id="cb5-7"><a href="#cb5-7" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>    data <span class="op">=</span> [<span class="dv">1</span>, <span class="dv">2</span>, <span class="va">None</span>, <span class="dv">4</span>]</span>
<span id="cb5-8"><a href="#cb5-8" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>    clean_data <span class="op">=</span> preprocess_data(data)</span>
<span id="cb5-9"><a href="#cb5-9" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>    <span class="bu">print</span>(clean_data)</span></code></pre></div>
